OmniUiCard.Name: ProfileCard

OmniDataTransformItem.Name: fscGetProfileCardDetails
OmniDataTransformItem.FormulaExpression: CONCAT(IF(HOUR(NOW()) <= 12, IF(HOUR(NOW()) == 0, "12", HOUR(NOW())), HOUR(NOW()) - 12), ":", IF(MINUTE(NOW()) < 10, CONCAT("0", MINUTE(NOW())), MINUTE(NOW())), IF(HOUR(NOW()) < 12, " AM", " PM"))
